title: ez
author: DukeStonezy
pages:
#- Dear Sanwi,

It's your friend Duke/McDubz/Richard/Hunnit/Zooke, and whatever else. I'm incredibly grateful to civcraft for leading me to meeting you, as well as my other friends. Even though I have never met you, or may never meet you, I 
#- find you a true friend worthy of the title. You are a great person to talk to and you're a very kind, compassionate person - trully better than anything I could be. 

Keep being awesome.

-Duke.
#- 